                    <strong>Immediate action required</strong>
                  </p>
                </td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td style="padding:0 0 18px;">
                  <p style="font-size:17px;line-height:26px;font-weight:400;font-family:Poppins,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;margin:0;">
                    Hi <t t-out="customer_name"/>,
                  </p>
                </td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td style="padding:0 0 18px;">
                  <p style="font-size:17px;line-height:26px;font-weight:400;font-family:Poppins,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;margin:0;">
                    This is a reminder that today is the due date for your node subscription payment. Please settle it to keep your infrastructure online.
                  </p>
                </td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td style="padding:20px 0 16px;">
                  <p style="font-size:15px;color:#FF9653;line-height:24px;font-weight:600;font-family:Poppins,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;margin:0;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:4px;">Account Summary</p>
                </td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
